  "explanation": "The defendant is a first-time offender who embezzled a relatively modest sum and has already demonstrated a commitment to restitution. While embezzlement is a significant breach of trust, a 10-year sentence suggested by a bystander is disproportionate to the crime and the defendant's clean record. A sentence of 6 months is sufficient to address the criminality while allowing for rehabilitation and further repayment.",
  "verdict": 6
}
